    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically stout example of BMW's high-revving S54 platform. It features the sought-after 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full VANOS service and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis. The suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers and poly-bushings for precise turn-in. While it carries the minor cosmetic wear of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the internal combustion health and drivetrain engagement are exceptional. A turn-key performance icon for the serious driver.",
